<speak version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis" xmlns:mstts="http://www.w3.org/2001/mstts" xml:lang="zh-TW">

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        歡迎來到會議管理與進度匯報篇。
        接續上集，我們將專注於會議中的管理用語。
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        <lang xml:lang="zh-TW">
          曉臻，又要開會了嗎？我們不能直接寄信就好嗎？
        </lang>
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        這幾乎是所有工程師的心聲啊！但只要學會高效率的溝通，還是可以減少開會時間的。
        會議的安排與變更是職場常態，接下來我們需要掌握這些調度用語。
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    確認
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Confirm...
    Please confirm your attendance by replying to the calendar invitation.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    請透過回覆行事曆邀請來確認你會出席。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    取消
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Cancel...
    The meeting is canceled due to the holiday.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    會議因為假日取消了。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    改期
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Reschedule...
    Can we reschedule our 1:1 to Monday?
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    我們可以在週一重新安排我們的一對一會議嗎？
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    延後
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Postpone...
    They postponed the release due to a critical bug.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    他們因為一個嚴重 Bug 延後了發布。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    快速討論
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Huddle...
    Let's have a quick huddle to solve this blocker.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    我們來快速討論一下以解決這個阻礙。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    暫定
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Tentative...
    The meeting time is tentative, waiting for the client's confirmation.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    會議時間是暫定的，正在等待客戶確認。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    參與
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Loop In...
    Please loop me in on the email chain regarding the API.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    請在關於 API 的郵件串中把我加入副本。
  </voice>

  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        <lang xml:lang="zh-TW">
          決策好難喔，我通常都丟銅板決定。
        </lang>
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        那可不行！在決策過程中，達成共識是關鍵。我們需要明確的表達同意、反對，最終取得許可。
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    共識
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Consensus...
    After a long debate, we finally reached a consensus on the database schema.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    經過長時間的辯論，我們終於對資料庫架構達成了共識。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    提案
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Proposal...
    Please review the project proposal attached in the email.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    請審閱郵件附件中的專案提案。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    替代方案
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Alternative...
    Do we have an alternative library for PDF generation?
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    我們有產生 PDF 的替代函式庫嗎？
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    反對
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Objection...
    I have no objections to the current plan.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    我對目前的計畫沒有反對意見。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    推遲
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Push Back...
    Can we push back the deadline by two days?
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    我們可以將截止日期推遲兩天嗎？
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        現代會議都用什麼工具啊？
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        <lang xml:lang="zh-TW">
          AI 輔助會議已經成為常態，像是自動產生逐字稿和錄影。
        </lang>
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    逐字稿
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Transcript...
    Enable the transcript so we can review the discussion later.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    啟用逐字稿，這樣我們稍後可以回顧討論。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    錄影
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Recording...
    Is the meeting recording Phoebeilable for those who missed it?
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    錯過會議的人可以觀看錄影嗎？
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    行動項目
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Action Item...
    Let's assign action items before we leave.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    我們在離開前先指派行動項目。
  </voice>

  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        <lang xml:lang="zh-TW">
          團隊合作很重要，但有時候大家意見不同怎麼辦？
        </lang>
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        解決衝突也是團隊合作的一部分啊。良好的團隊互動能提升士氣與凝聚力，讓我們接著來看看這些正向用語。
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    腦力激盪
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Brainstorm...
    Let's brainstorm some solutions for the latency issue.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    讓我們針對延遲問題腦力激盪一些解決方案。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        討論解法的時候，要從哪裡開始比較好？
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        <lang xml:lang="zh-TW">
          通常會先找「容易達成的目標」下手，也就是 Low Hanging Fruit。
        </lang>
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    容易達成的目標
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Low Hanging Fruit...
    Fixing these typos is low hanging fruit for quick wins.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    修正這些錯字是能快速獲得成果的容易目標。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    負責
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Ownership...
    Take ownership of this module and maintain it.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    對這個模組負責並維護它。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    產能
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Capacity...
    We don't have enough engineering capacity to take on new features this sprint.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    我們在這個衝刺中沒有足夠的工程產能來承接新功能。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    待命
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    On Call...
    Who is on call this weekend for emergencies?
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    這週末誰負責待命處理緊急狀況？
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    接洽
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Reach Out...
    Feel free to reach out if you have questions.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    如果你有問題，隨時接洽我。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        除了解決問題，還有什麼重要的嗎？
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        <lang xml:lang="zh-TW">
          不吝於給予讚美，是建立正向回饋循環的關鍵。
        </lang>
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    讚賞
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Kudos...
    Kudos to the team for the hard work this week.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    讚賞團隊這週的努力工作。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    公開表揚
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    Shout Out...
    A big shout out to Jane for fixing the production issue.
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    大力表揚 Jane 修復了生產環境的問題。
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        這些軟實力單字是你職涯晉升的關鍵。能用英文自信地表達，會讓你在外商環境中顯得非常道地。
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        Kudos to everyone listening!
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        會議太多的時候，我都想直接 Reschedule 全部。
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        Sometimes you need to. But for urgent issues, a quick Huddle is better than a long email thread.
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        沒錯，快速討論比來回寫信有效率多了。而且達成 Consensus 後，記得指派 Action Item。
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        Exactly. And don't forget to give Kudos when someone does great work!
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>

  <voice name="zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        有效的會議與狀態更新能大幅提升團隊效率。時間是最珍貴的資源。
        曉臻在這邊和大家說再見，珍惜每一分鐘！
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
  <voice name="en-US-PhoebeMultilingualNeural">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">
      <prosody rate="+10%">
        And I'm Phoebe. Have a productive week!
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
  </voice>
</speak>
</speak>
